If they don’t want to accept us as Macedonia, we can resort to other countries, such as China and Russia, and be part of Eurasian integration.”
Prime Minister Zaev says the accession to NATO will be accompanied by more than necessary investments in Macedonia, which has an unemployment rate of more than 20%.
